title: Back to Back Beef
itunes:title: Back to Back Beef
description:
07/18/16 Starting the week off with back to back beef, but with different scenarios. Kim K took the beef to higher heights between Kanye and Taylor Swift when she leaked audio of the two musicians conversation but ended up falling short when Kim and her husband became Donkey of the Day. As for Drake and Joe Budden it looks like the beef between the two will never rest as they had back to back diss records for each other.
